sourcesContent: import React, {Component} from "react" import {Link} from "react-router-dom" export default class AdminTableRow extends Component { render() { const { product_id, name, colour, size, price, gender, category, brand, current_stock, } = this.props.products; return ( {product_id} {name} {colour} {size} {price} {gender} {category} {brand} {current_stock} Edit Delete ) } }
